sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant View (Blade)
    participant Controller
    participant Model
    participant Database

    User->>View (Blade): Submits Post Form
    View (Blade)->>Controller: POST /posts (content, user_id)
    Controller->>Controller: Validate Input
    Controller->>Model: Post::create()
    Model->>Database: INSERT INTO posts
    Database-->>Model: Return Post ID
    Model-->>Controller: Post Instance
    Controller-->>View (Blade): Redirect & Success Flash
    View (Blade)-->>User: Unread post displayed in feed
